data.description: Immerse yourself in the charm of this 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home that finds its haven on a tranquil street. Designed for the immediate family but also perfect for gatherings, the open concept floor plan features a kitchen overlooking the family room while additional formal areas add to the entertaining space. The heart of this home gleams with a recent renovation, boasting gleaming granite countertops, sleek cabinetry, and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances.  Step into the embrace of comfort with gleaming ceramic tile floors flowing seamlessly throughout, a haven for allergy sufferers and pet lovers alike. Find your sanctuary in the spacious master suite, tucked away from the bustle of family life, featuring a luxurious walk-in closet and a spa-inspired bathroom with dual sinks. Unwind under the canopy of your private gazebo, a tranquil oasis in your expansive fenced backyard, perfect for grilling with friends or stargazing.  Enjoy the peace of mind knowing the AC, windows, doors, and hot water heater were all replaced in 2016, and the brand new roof keeps you protected for years to come.    Save on your water bill with the well that provides irrigation  .  Live life to the fullest with vibrant downtown Clermont, the Florida Turnpike, championship golf courses, and shopping all within a quick drive, offering endless possibilities for adventure and convenience. Don't miss your chance to call this picture-perfect haven your own, schedule your showing today.
